 "A case study is a device that provides learners \nwith a simulation that has an educational basis. It takes a situation, generally \nbased in reality, and asks learners to demonstrate or describe what action they \nwould take to complete a task or resolve a situation. The case study allows \nlearners apply their own knowledge and experience to completing the tasks \nassigned. when designing a case study consider the following:<ul> \n<li>\tWhat educational points are conveyed in the story<\/li>\n<li>\tWhat preparation will the learners need to do prior to working on the \ncase study<\/li>\n<li>\tWhere the case study fits into the rest of the course<\/li>\n<li>\tHow the learners will interact with the materials and each other e.g.\nif run in a classroom situation can teams be setup to work on different aspects\nof the case and if so how are ideas feed back to the class<\/li><\/ul>": "T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp m\u00f4 ph\u1ecfng c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi h\u1ecdc sinh\n ph\u1ea3i minh h\u1ecda ho\u1eb7c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng.\nT\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecdc sinh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \n\u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao. Khi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau \u0111\u00e2y:<ul> \n<li>\tC\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng<\/li>\n<li>\tH\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/li>\n<li>\tT\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/li>\n<li>\tH\u1ecdc sinh s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.\nN\u1ebfu di\u1ec5n ra trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n nh\u00f3m theo c\u00e1c kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c nhau c\u1ee7a t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng\nv\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec c\u00e1c \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p \u00fd ra sao<\/li><\/ul>", 
