 "<p>If left unchecked a small number of spelling and capitalization errors will be accepted. If checked only an exact match in spelling and capitalization will be accepted.<\/p><p><strong>For example:<\/strong> If the correct answer is <code>Elephant<\/code> then both <code>elephant<\/code> and <code>Eliphant<\/code> will be judged <em>\"close enough\"<\/em> by the algorithm as it only has one letter wrong, even if \"Check Capitilization\" is on.<\/p><p>If capitalization checking is off in the above example, the lowercase <code>e<\/code> will not be considered a mistake and <code>eliphant<\/code> will also be accepted.<\/p><p>If both \"Strict Marking\" and \"Check Capitalization\" are set, the only correct answer is \"Elephant\". If only \"Strict Marking\" is checked and \"Check Capitalization\" is not, \"elephant\" will also be accepted.<\/p>": "<p> N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ed7i nh\u1ecf v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea3 ho\u1eb7c ch\u1eef hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn, c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00fang ph\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea3 l\u1eabn ch\u1eef hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p><p><strong>V\u00ed d\u1ee5:<\/strong> N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1p \u00e1n l\u00e0 <code>Elephant<\/code> th\u00ec c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi <code>elephant<\/code> v\u00e0 <code>Eliphant<\/code> s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00e0<em>\"g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00fang\"<\/em> v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 sai m\u1ed9t k\u00fd t\u1ef1, ngay c\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn \"Ch\u1eef hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng\" \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn.<\/p><p>N\u1ebfu trong v\u00ed d\u1ee5 tr\u00ean, t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn  \"Ch\u1eef hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng\" kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, ch\u1eef <code>e<\/code> s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 sai v\u00e0 <code>eliphant<\/code> c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00fang.<\/p><p>N\u1ebfu ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea3 hai t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn \"Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i\" v\u00e0 \"Ch\u1eef hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng\" , th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0  \"Elephant\". N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecdn \"Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i\" v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn \"ch\u0169 hoa ch\u1eef th\u01b0\u1eddng\" , \"elephant\" c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang.<\/p>", 
